<para><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1PrimitiveVisual" kindref="compound">PrimitiveVisual</ref> <ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1PrimitiveVisual_1_1Property" kindref="compound">Property</ref>. </para>
